
Changing the analog input voltage results in corresponding changes in the
displayed ADC values.

---

## Testing & Verification

The implementation was tested on hardware using:
- Serial terminal output (PuTTY)
- Real-time ADC value updates

Optional verification using oscilloscope or demonstration video may be included
in the repository.

---

## Tools Used

- STM32CubeIDE
- PuTTY (Serial Terminal)
- GitHub

